      "shard_upgrade": "When Meat Hook hits an enemy, it deals bonus damage based on the distance pulled.<br><br>When Meat Hook hits an ally, Meat Hook's cooldown is reduced by %cooldown_reduction_pct_allied_hook%%%.",
